line_1: At last the ruddy sun quite sunk,
From scribbling for hire, when my credit is sunk,
line_2: To buy a new coat, and to line an old trunk:

line_1: In Public rage all private Love was sunk,
line_2: With zeal for Party, and with Passion drunk,

line_1: Alas how chang'd! how are the mighty sunk,
line_2: From the firm Patriot to the whining Monk!
